title: The Forgotten UFO Crash - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 3/16/22
itunes:title: The Forgotten UFO Crash - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 3/16/22
description:
George Noory and researchers Paola Harris and Jacques Vallee explore evidence of a little known UFO crash in New Mexico in 1945, two years before the more famous Roswell UFO crash, and whether it could be connected to nuclear bomb tests conducted in the area after World War II.
